	<header class="entry-header"> 
	     <h1 class="entry-title"></h1> 
	</header><!-- .entry-header --> 

	<div class="entry-content">		
		<p>Hi, my name is Mike Kurz. I&#8217;m a freelance journalist and blogger who writes about technology, gaming, and unique products. The topics I write about also happen to be passions of mine outside of my writing career, so it&#8217;s pretty safe to say that I know what I&#8217;m talking about. (They say write what you know, right?)</p>
<p>You may have seen my work on Android Rundown, Incredible Things, Games Are Evil or number of other websites.</p>
<div style="width: 300px; float: left; margin: 0 20px 0 0"><a href="http://www.androidrundown.com/author/michael-kurz/" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://www.androidrundown.com']);"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-32" title="androidrundown" src="http://whatthegeek.net/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/androidrundown.jpg" alt="" width="205" height="82" /></a></div>
<div style="width: 300px; float: left; margin: 0 20px 0 0;"><a href="http://www.incrediblethings.com/author/whatthegeek/" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://www.incrediblethings.com']);"><img src="http://whatthegeek.net/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/IT-logo.jpg" alt="IT-logo" width="205" height="88" /></a></div>
<div style="width: 300px; float: left;"><a href="http://gamesareevil.com/author/michael/" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://gamesareevil.com']);"><img src="http://whatthegeek.net/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/games-are-evil-logo1.jpg" alt="games-are-evil-logo" width="205" height="78" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-296" /></a></div>
