<li><a href="http://www.quora.com/Video-Games/What-are-the-best-video-games-of-2012/answer/Mike-Kurz" class="rsswidget" title='&lt;div style="color: #666666"&gt;In Video Games: Mike Kurz added this answer.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div id="ld_xfoqkf_1805"&gt;&lt;div style="font-weight: bold; color: #000000"&gt;&lt;div class="hover_menu hidden hover_menu_wide hover_menu_cards" style="display: none" id="__w2_kXiVHYU_menu"&gt;&lt;div class="hover_menu_nub"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="hover_menu_contents" id="__w2_kXiVHYU_menu_contents"&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;a class="user" href="/Mike-Kurz" action_mousedown="UserLinkClickthrough" id="__w2_kXiVHYU_link"&gt;Mike Kurz&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;2012 has been a great year for games. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Kingdoms of Amalur: Reckoning was a great RPG despite the fate of the studio that put it together. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;If you&amp;#039;re into Extreme Sports, SSX brought something new to the table with a wide variety of asynchronous multiplayer features. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Diablo III is a triumph of a game if you&amp;#039;re into dungeon crawling and clicking things to &lt;span class="qlink_container"&gt;&lt;a href="/Death-and-Dying-1"&gt;death&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;. That&amp;#039;s sort of a reductive summary of the game, but I&amp;#039;ve got a lot of ground to cover here. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Borderlands 2 improved on the original in just about every way, and it&amp;#039;s well worth your time. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;X-Com Enemy Unknown is an excellent strategy game. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Dishonored really cranked up the volume on player agency in stealth games&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Assassin&amp;#039;s Creed III has some problems, but it tells a great story and hey, you can kill redcoats with a tomahawk. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Need for Speed Most Wanted is a great racing game.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&amp;nbsp;If you prefer your racing games full of crashes and mayhem, it&amp;#039;s the racing game for you. If you prefer a little more precision, check out Forza Horizon - also a great game. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Halo 4 is a very methodical shooter, and a very well crafted game. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;If you prefer your shooters fast and loose, Black Ops II is a solid installment in the series. Treyarch didn&amp;#039;t make any &lt;span class="qlink_container"&gt;&lt;a href="/Earth"&gt;earth&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; shattering changes to the CoD formula but the changes they made might make you rethink the way you approach CoD.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a style="font-weight: bold" href="http://www.quora.com/Video-Games/What-are-the-best-video-games-of-2012"&gt;See question on Quora&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;'>What are the best video games of 2012?</a></li>
